@startuml
!include ../../styles/plantuml-theme.puml

left to right direction
title FIG-08-04. Online Store order data flow

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam nodesep 90
skinparam ranksep 70

rectangle "Customer\n<<External entity>>" as Customer #FFFFFF
rectangle "Capture order\n<<Process>>" as Capture #EAF6E8
rectangle "Authorise payment\n<<Process>>" as PaymentProcess #EAF6E8
rectangle "Create shipment request\n<<Process>>" as ShipmentProcess #EAF6E8
database "Order data\n<<Data store>>" as OrderStore #F2F5F7
rectangle "Payment Provider System\n<<External system>>" as PaymentProvider #FFF4D6
rectangle "Delivery Partner System\n<<External system>>" as DeliveryPartner #FFF4D6

Customer --> Capture : Order details
Capture -right-> PaymentProcess : Order total
PaymentProcess -right-> ShipmentProcess : Paid order

Capture -right-> OrderStore : Order draft
PaymentProcess -right-> PaymentProvider : Payment exchange
PaymentProcess -right-> OrderStore : Payment status
ShipmentProcess -right-> DeliveryPartner : Shipment exchange
ShipmentProcess -right-> OrderStore : Shipment status

note bottom
  DFD view.
  Arrows show data movement and transformation, not process sequence ownership,
  database schema or software deployment.
end note
@enduml
